TVS Motor has announced the launch of the new TVS iQube Electric scooter in three avatars that come loaded with best-in-class on-road range of 140 km. A host of intelligent connected features such as 7” TFT touchscreen, voice assist and TVS iQube Alexa skillset, intuitive music player control, fast charging with a plug-and-play carry along charger, 32 litre under-seat storage and much more are on offer. 

 

Mr. Sudarshan Venu, Managing Director, TVS Motor Company, said, “The launch of the new TVS iQube is a testament to our commitment of offering world-class EV technology with never-before intelligent and personalised connected experience. TVS Motor has been investing in electric technologies for more than ten years now, and TVS iQube has provided thousands of our customers with an unparalleled electric riding experience. TVS Motor will continue to scale new benchmarks in connected mobility and EV with our innovations and advanced technology offerings.”

#TVSMotorCompany #TVSiQubeElectric #FutureMobility #EV

We are redefining the formula of mobility with simplicity of 1-2-3. Stay tuned to know more!
#ThePowerOf123 #TVSiQubeElectric #TVSiQube #TvsMotorCompany

We are the pioneers of an integrated Approach in Science and Technology for a Sustainable Future. The Smart X Talk feature in the TVS connect app reminds the rider to switch on the INTELLIGO feature from the settings whenever their bike is idle for 30 seconds. The Idle Start and Stop technology shut down the engine after a seven-second countdown which saves fuel.
This Technology Day we celebrate the amalgamation of sustainability and technology.
.
.
.
This feature is available on TVS NTORQ XT 125

Petronas becomes title partner for TVS Racing, India’s first factory racing team in a landmark agreement. The team will be rebranded Petronas TVS Racing Team with a brand new livery and will use high-performance engine oils from Petronas in all racing disciplines.

#TVSMotorCompany #TVSRacing #Petronas

We are happy to be acknowledged by visiting UK Prime Minister, Boris Johnson, in reference to strong trade ties between the United Kingdom and  India. We are also happy to announce our total investment of £100 million in Norton Motorcycles leading to creation of world class products and a push towards electrification and sustainability.

#TVSMotorCompany #NortonMotorcycles
Let's accelerate our transition towards a renewable economy, as we invest together. #WorldEarthDay2022 #EarthDay

TVS Racing makes a historic announcement with the first ever TVS Asia One Make Championship. This global milestone makes TVS Motor Company the first Indian manufacturer to conduct an Asia One Make Championship. Join us as B Selvaraj, Team Manager, TVS Racing gives us a walkthrough of a specially developed race-spec RR310 for the Asia One Make Championship. Sixteen riders, eight international and eight from the Indian One Make Championship, will take part over four rounds of the championship in 2022. Stay tuned to our channels for more. 

 

#TVSMotorCompany #TVSRacing #TVSApache #RR310 #ARRC

TVS Motor Company grows its global footprint with the acquisition of UK based e-bike brand EBCO. This marks another step for TVS Motor towards leading the sustainable personal mobility space in Europe. #TVSMotorCompany #eBike #Mobility

It has been quite a month for TVS with awards, milestones and customer-love just piling on like blessings. These achievements validate all the work we have put into building a trustworthy brand, and motivate us to take bigger strides with our offerings to you. #Happenings@TVS

The people who love you want to see you come home safe. This National Road Safety Month, let's commit to responsible choices—for ourselves and for those who matter most. Let's pledge to never drink and drive.

Stay responsible, stay safe.

#DriveSafe #RoadSafetyMonth #TVSMotor #Safety #RSEL

Think of your seat belt as a hug from safety itself! Every time you buckle up, you’re protecting yourself and your loved ones. Fasten up, drive safe, and ensure every trip ends with a happy return. 

Let’s make every journey a safe one.

#TVSMotor #Safety #RSEL #RoadSafetyMonth

Your safety starts with a simple step – wear a helmet every ride, every time! 

This Road Safety Month, let’s pledge to protect ourselves and our loved ones by making helmets a non-negotiable habit. Because every ride deserves a safe return.

#TVSMotor #Safety #RSEL #RoadSafetyMonth

We are thrilled to announce our entry into #Morocco, marking another significant step in our journey to bring innovative, sustainable mobility solutions to global markets.

In collaboration with MotorSports Maroc, operating under the retail banner of Hindi Motors, we are introducing an exciting lineup of two-wheelers: TVS Apache 160 & 200, TVS NTORQ 125, TVS Raider 125

With over 58 million users globally, TVS Motor Company is proud to offer engineering excellence and a great ownership experience, now to customers in Morocco.

Together with Hindi Motors, we are committed to shaping the future of mobility and empowering communities across the globe.

#TVSMotorCompany #Innovation #GlobalExpansion #Morocco #SustainableMobility #EngineeringExcellence

We were honoured to host Shri Nitin Gadkari, Hon’ble Union Minister of Road Transport and Highways and other Government of India dignitaries at the TVS Motor Company stall at Bharat Mobility Global Expo 2025.

Our leadership had the privilege of showcasing our innovative mobility concepts designed and made in India for the world. The concepts along with our EV and green fuel range of products reflect our commitment towards Government of India’s sustainability goals, development of cutting-edge technology, and engineering excellence in India.

Hon’ble Minister appreciated TVS safety initiatives for Children’s Helmet, underscoring our dedication to safer road travel for the next generation.

#TVSMotorCompany #FutureMobility #BharatMobility2025 #Sustainability #Innovation #Roadsafety #RSEL #Leadership

Delighted to host Shri Amitabh Kant, G20 Sherpa of India, and Former CEO NITI Aayog, at the TVS Motor Company stall during Bharat Mobility 2025. He witnessed our commitment to sustainable urban mobility with electric vehicles, advanced technology, and green solutions.

TVS Motor stands proud in driving India’s leadership in global mobility with sustainability at its core and aligned with the "Make in India" vision.

#BharatMobility2025 #SustainableMobility #MakeInIndia #GreenMobility #FutureOfTransportation #TVSMotor #Innovation

We were privileged to welcome Shri H.D. Kumaraswamy, Hon’ble Union Cabinet Minister of Heavy Industries, and Minister of Steel, Government of India, NITI Aayog Advisor Mr. Sudhendu J. Sinha, Dr. Hanif Qureshi, IPS - Additional Secretary, Ministry of Heavy Industries and other Government of India dignitaries to our stall at Bharat Mobility 2025.

Our leadership team had the opportunity to showcase TVS Motor’s green mobility solutions, including the PM-eDrive-approved TVS iQube, as well as our innovative ethanol and CNG products. Privileged to showcase scaling up of Hon'ble Prime Minister’s vision of designed and Made in India for the world through these initiatives. These pioneering efforts underscore our steadfast commitment to driving transformation through sustainable and future-ready technologies.

#BharatMobility2025 #SustainableMobility #Innovation #TVSMotor #RSEL

Redefining Urban Mobility: TVS Motor Company proudly unveils the TVS King EV MAX, India's first Bluetooth-connected passenger electric three-wheeler!

Key Features:

- TVS SmartXonnect™ for real-time navigation, diagnostics & alerts
- Range: 179 km on a single charge
- Quick Charging: 2 hours 15 minutes (0-80%)
- Top Speed: 60 km/h
- Warranty: 6 years/150,000 km

Designed for sustainability, performance, and passenger comfort, the King EV MAX is the perfect companion for urban commuters and fleet operators alike. Currently available in UP, Bihar, J&K, Delhi, and West Bengal, this connected EV will soon hit roads across India. 

Let’s accelerate the transition to clean mobility together!

#TVSMotor #KingEVMAX #ElectricMobility #SustainableFuture #Innovation #RSEL #RedefineMobility
